{"tid":1217167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「支持愛國人士」【逃犯條例】美眾議員：國會擬推《香港人權與民主法案》","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:00:35.000Z","uid":36470,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3e563bae72b9b96af7b1d7c1851357abdf0b7f","tid":1217167,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>支持愛國人士身體力行 世世代代都留係中國 為中國美好將來出一分力！</strong><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例】美眾議員：國會擬推《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n即時國際<br />\n<br />\n香港政府修訂《逃犯條例》所產生的爭議，引發國際社會關注。美國眾議院中國事務委員會（Joint China Commission）主席麥戈文（Jim McGovern）發布Twitter表示，本周將提出《香港人權與民主法案》（Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act）。<br />\n<br />\n播放<br />\n麥戈文於當地時間周三（12日）就港府修訂《逃犯條例》所引發的爭議發布5條Twitter，稱「如果《逃犯條例》通過，國會須修改1992年通過的《香港政策法》（United States&ndash;Hong Kong Policy Act），以回應自治的腐敗。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRep. Jim McGovern<br />\n✔<br />\n@RepMcGovern<br />\n &middot; 21小時<br />\n回覆給 @RepMcGovern<br />\n4/ Strong protections for human rights and rule of law are the foundation of Hong Kong&rsquo;s prosperity &amp; flourishing U.S.-Hong Kong relations. If the extradition law passes, Congress must look to revise the Hong Kong Policy Act of 1992 to reflect the erosion of autonomy.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRep. Jim McGovern<br />\n✔<br />\n@RepMcGovern<br />\n5/5 This week I will join @marcorubio &amp; @RepChrisSmith in introducing the &ldquo;HK Human Rights &amp; Democracy Act&rdquo; to reaffirm U.S. commitment to human rights &amp; the rule of law at a time when Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy is imperiled by Chinese gov't interference &amp; a revised #ExtraditionLaw.<br />\n<br />\n麥戈文表示，本周將聯同共和黨參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）以及共和黨眾議員史密斯（Chris Smith）提出《香港人權與民主法案》，重申美國對人權和法治的承諾。該法案設置的目的，是對涉及鎮壓香港民主的香港或中國內地的政府官員，設立懲罰機制，包括禁止涉事官員入境美國及凍結其在美資產。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，與香港民眾站於同一陣線，指《逃犯條例》會令當地人權人士、商人、記者和美國公民或被引渡到中國。他呼籲行政長官林鄭月娥及立法會主席梁君彥撤回有關法例，另外尋求方案保留香港自治，保障人權及法治。<br />\n<br />\n麥戈文並呼籲警務署及保安局下令警方勿使用過份武力，保障市民表達言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/340062/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A8-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F340062%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258E%25A8-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjfZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=a2c9cb55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/340062/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A8-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88</a>"},{"pid":"d5ff93ac42d367769543ecb4a184a021db860278","tid":1217167,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"#LOVE &amp; PEACE"},{"pid":"e5d55e4d4c1ee2d2d6a5eb1247889d516c263cf2","tid":1217167,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"SUPPORT"},{"pid":"14a4e4f5fe8915f1f5ba946000510d4c265d1efa","tid":1217167,"uid":78470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"仲有狗官班屋企人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537c853c6a0ad9385e1a86b0dc45a184368c4247","tid":1217167,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"比多啲美國百姓欣賞香港警察嘅英姿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901